abstract: Rio Grande files to Dec. 1 were received here to-day. The Tamaulipas insurgents, under VARGAS, COBOLLOX and others, were very active, but as yet had made no movement of much military importance. The small and isolated bodies of State forces are unable to cope with them, but ESCOBEDO is marching with the Third Division of the rational army on Matamoros, where he will reorganize for a vigorous campaign.
